casebody.data:
STATE EX REL. NEGUSE
v.
CRAWFORD 2019-0315 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 8, 2019

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On appellant's memorandum in support of jurisdiction. This cause originated in the court of appeals and should proceed as an appeal of right pursuant to S.Ct.Prac.R. 5.01. The clerk shall issue an order for the transmission of the record from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct. Prac.R. 16.02 through 16.07.
